lyrics:
[Verse]
And I'm tired of hearing this crap
Cause you're never coming back
You can leave me now, just like that
Just what I needed, another heart attack

[Chorus]
You've got to know it's so deceiving
The way you play with my feelings, it's unbelieving
But I've had enough, I'm finally leaving
No more more tears, I'll be free and breathing
